data.description: Super clean 1.5-sty w/ 2 car garage, full basement, and nice 50 x 126 lot! Brand new roof and vinyl siding installed in 2024! Freshly painted interior, hardwood floors, and tons of natural light throughout! Super clean basement featuring Rec Room with new vinyl flooring! Updated plumbing and HWT! Bathroom with solid surface surround! Newer electrical panel and lots of new lighting throughout! Move-in-condition and priced to sell! Original windows and a gravity furnace. Selling AS IS- Better hurry won't last!
